y%20and%20memorization.%20You%20use%20your%20Intelligence%20whenever%20a%20spell%20refers%20to%20your%20spellcasting%20ability.%20In%20addition%2C%20you%20use%20your%20Intelligence%20modifier%20when%20setting%20the%20saving%20throw%20DC%20for%20a%20wizard%20spell%20you%20cast%20and%20when%20making%20an%20attack%20roll%20with%20one.%5Cn%5CnSpell%20save%20DC%20%3D%208%20%2B%20your%20proficiency%20bonus%20%2B%20your%20Intelligence%20modifier%5Cn%5CnSpell%20attack%20modifier%20%3D%20your%20proficiency%20bonus%20%2B%20your%20Intelligence%20modifier%5Cn%5CnRitual%20Casting%5Cn%5CnYou%20can%20cast%20a%20wizard%20spell%20as%20a%20ritual%20if%20that%20spell%20has%20the%20ritual%20tag%20and%20you%20have%20the%20spell%20in%20your%20spellbook.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20have%20the%20spell%20prepared.%5Cn%5CnSpellcasting%20Focus%5Cn%5CnYou%20can%20use%20an%20arcane%20focus%20as%20a%20spellcasting%20focus%20for%20your%20wizard%20spells.%5Cn%5CnLearning%20Spells%20of%201st%20Level%20and%20Higher%5Cn%5CnEach%20time%20you%20gain%20a%20wizard%20level%2C%20you%20can%20add%20two%20wizard%20spells%20of%20your%20choice%20to%20your%20spellbook%20for%20free.%20Each%20of%20these%20spells%20must%20be%20of%20a%20level%20for%20which%20you%20have%20spell%20slots%2C%20as%20shown%20on%20the%20Wizard%20table.%5Cn%5CnOn%20your%20adventures%2C%20you%20might%20find%20other%20spells%20that%20you%20can%20add%20to%20your%20spellbook%20(see%20the%20%5C%22Your%20Spellbook%5C%22%20sidebar).%5Cn%22%2C%22trackedId%22%3Anull%2C%22isTracked%22%3Afalse%2C%22tracked%22%3Anull%7D%2C%7B%22characterId%22%3A%2272c78b1e-45ef-4af4-a562-ab220bf3bafb%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22Arcane%20Recovery%20(Wizard%2C%20Lvl.%201)%22%2C%22level%22%3A1%2C%22characterClass%22%3A%22Wizard%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22You%20have%20learned%20to%20regain%20some%20of%20your%20magical%20energy%20by%20studying%20your%20spellbook.%20Once%20per%20day%20when%20you%20finish%20a%20short%20rest%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20expended%20spell%20slots%20to%20